<p><b>Christopher "Chris" Meledandri</b> (born May 15, 1959) is an American <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Film_producer" title="Film producer">film producer</a>, and the founder (2007) and CEO of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Illumination_Entertainment" title="Illumination Entertainment">Illumination Entertainment</a>.</p>
<p></p>
